title: The Hidden Curricula of Education w/ Professor Douglas Kellner (UCLA)

tags: Why Do We Go To School?
description:
Viewers of this channel will recognize Douglas Kellner as a co-host of ALTERNATIVE VIEWS TV (https://archive.org/details/alternative_views). Douglas Kellner, Professor George F. Kneller Philosophy of Education Chair at UCLA, describes the hidden curriculum in modern education. Schooling tends to be a conservative force; it propagates the status quo. What can we do to make education more progressive?

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
